{"tid":2247176,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如何給年輕人希望 - 陳惜姿","createTime":"2020-10-17T15:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T16:26:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2eac752ab61b8fe367936974a85920d6ab8b894","tid":2247176,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201017/3RLEEGLT75FMPB4TK4IQEQA6IU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201017%2F3RLEEGLT75FMPB4TK4IQEQA6IU%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPQ4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=5ef85af0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201017%2F3RLEEGLT75FMPB4TK4IQEQA6IU%2F&h=1bb32461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201017/3RLEEGLT75FMPB4TK4IQEQA6IU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n如何給年輕人希望 - 陳惜姿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JFqx_Eq8McDU2PXdVsfjVyd1yyw=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EE4X72GIWFDXDFFK3XYLBOUKP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJFqx_Eq8McDU2PXdVsfjVyd1yyw%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEE4X72GIWFDXDFFK3XYLBOUKP4.jpg&h=e6cf5010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽一位中學老師說，上屆文憑試考生選科，以醫護、治療學系為主，更有學生分數未達理工三寶之一的物理治療系，最後寧願選東華學院的物理治療，也不選八大其他學位，叫人大感意外。如此選科原因只有一個，這些專業有利移民。<br />\n<br />\n我納悶，十八歲青年有這麼實際？是父母的意思？抑或只是老師的主觀視角？連未入大學的年輕人都想着離開，這城還留下什麼。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n現實情況，年輕人看在眼裏，路是難走，但他們總得起步。在大學資訊日，有機會聽到自己教了兩年的學生分享，他們積極正面，意志堅定，反過來竟鼓勵了我。當我們經常唉聲嘆氣，問傳媒這一行要怎樣走下去。快要畢業的學生考慮過後，眼神篤定，堅決跟大家說她仍想跑新聞、做記者，我們應該鼓勵，而非皺眉。<br />\n<br />\n今年傳媒不算好景，但問過一些畢業生，想做記者的原來都有着落，又不算太差。疫情下百業蕭條，傳媒已比下有餘。還有一點，現在入行，是大時代下的記者，見證一個急劇轉變的社會。這種經驗，換一個角度看，也彌足珍貴。"},{"pid":"2b8f5f27ee00bb1e9e12b43274190ff3bf03313e","tid":2247176,"uid":22329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"先唔講技術移民，依家fg有幾多工種，可以起薪高過PT。又唔洗驚比人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2b4b97e6ed28b11ce5c96249d553495fd66015","tid":2247176,"uid":3112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b8f5f27ee00bb1e9e12b43274190ff3bf03313e","tid":2247176,"uid":22329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"先唔講技術移民，依家fg有幾多工種，可以起薪高過PT。又唔洗驚比人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"應該話依家出面既starting/job security有邊度可以比得上MPS-based既同等職位？<br />\n<br />\n出面做admin同入面做EO<br />\n出面做19文員仔同入面做ACO/CA<br />\n。。。<br />\n得出面做醫療拍得住，甚至正過入面做醫療咋<br />\n咁玩法，叫啲人點樣唔狗衝醫療科？"}]}